              "loglevel": "INFO",
              "data_body": "{\"traceId\":\"453460-10.22.119.112-1203-1782787496078-343\",\"extParam\":{\"robotWeworkId\":\"30289056\",\"leaseHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-private-domain-lease.ke.com\",\"houseId\":\"106118036896\",\"contactInfo\":\"{\\\"address\\\":\\\"金牛区抚琴小区4，5，6组2幢6单元408号\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"黄文帅\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"139****5399\\\"}\",\"cityCode\":\"510100\",\"groupId\":\"10814164336933678\",\"aiRobotUcId\":1000000031653787,\"msgId\":\"4048760\",\"datacenterHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-cloudkeeper-datacenter.ke.com\",\"latestMsgId\":\"4048760\",\"ruleHost\":\"http://rule.cloudkeeper.huiju.ke.com\",\"msgTime\":1782787495000,\"senderType\":5,\"aiRobotUserId\":\"31653787\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606202295\",\"atList\":\"\"},\"cityCode\":\"510100\",\"groupId\":\"10814164336933678\",\"className\":\"com.ke.huiju.cloudkeeper.support.vo.fact.ServiceKeeperFact\",\"isConfident\":\"0\",\"sessionId\":\"new_session_id:SERVICE_KEEPER--GROUP_CHAT--10814164336933678--1#1782787495000\",\"aiInvolve\":\"0\",\"businessScene\":1,\"firstTrigger\":1,\"requestId\":\"4048760\",\"senderType\":5,\"serviceId\":\"private-domain-lease\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606202295\",\"sessionInitiator\":5,\"matchingPlan\":\"GENERAL\",\"isInfoComplete\":\"0\",\"messageContent\":\"亲爱的租客小伙伴🥳\n欢迎入驻贝壳省心租的温馨小窝🏠，今天可是个超棒的日子，房子正式交付给您啦！\n--------------------------------\n当您完成缴费后，系统会把门锁的初始密码发送到您签约时留的手机号上，您可得留意查收哦～\n--------------------------------\n🔐修改密码：打开贝壳找房APP，用签约手机号登录→依次点击【我的】进入【租约】→【智能门锁】→【密码管理】→输入新密码，原密码自动失效。（要是没收到短信发的密码，就得瞅瞅是不是费用还没交完哦~） \n--------------------------------\n🔔以后若是没有按时缴纳租金，系统将会自动冻结门锁密码哦，不过别担心，缴费后半小时就会自动解冻～\n--------------------------------\n📌更多门锁常见问题，可点击这里：#小程序://贝壳找房丨二手房新房租房装修/门锁问题指引/vTpTJ23cPvIirig\n\n愿每一次暖灯长明，照亮您奔赴理想的漫漫征途哇✨！\"}",
